    <h1 align="center" class="card-style">U.S. Federal Laws</h1>

    <button onclick="topFunction()" id="my_btn" title="Go to top">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_upward</span>
    </button>

    <div class="accordion card-img-cntr-toggle" id="accordionE">
      <div class="card"> <!-- 1st -->
        <div class="card-header  card-header-odd" id="heading1">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
            <h4>Civil Rights Act of 1964</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse1" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading1" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-odd">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/civilrightsact.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Forbids discrimination on the grounds of race, color, religion, sex, or national origin.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 2nd -->
        <div class="card-header card-header-even" id="heading2">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
            <h4>The Voting Rights Act of 1965</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse2" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading2" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-even">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/votingrights.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Forbids racial discrimination in elections, and it has been modified several times to provide protections against other types of voter discrimination.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 3rd -->
        <div class="card-header  card-header-odd" id="heading3">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left tab-heading-even collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
            <h4>Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA)</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-odd">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/ada.gif"/>
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Forbids discrimination against people with impairments in telecommunications, public accommodations, employment, and other areas.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 4th -->
        <div class="card-header card-header-even" id="heading2">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
            <h4>Clean Air Act</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse4" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading4" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-even">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/clean_air.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Controls air pollutants and establishes standards for air quality in order to safeguard the environment and general public’s health.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 5th -->
        <div class="card-header  card-header-odd" id="heading5">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left tab-heading-even collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
            <h4>Occupational Safety and Health Act (OSHA)</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading5" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-odd">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/osha.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Mandates that companies maintain a safe and healthy workplace and establishes requirements for such conditions.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 6th -->
        <div class="card-header card-header-even" id="heading2">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
            <h4>Fair Labor Standard Act (FLSA)</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse6" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading6" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-even">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/flsa.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Regulates child labor, establishes minimum wage, and overtime pay regulations.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 7th -->
        <div class="card-header  card-header-odd" id="heading7">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left tab-heading-even collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7">
            <h4>Social Security Act</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse7" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading7" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-odd">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/socialsecurity.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Established a social insurance program to provide retirement, disability, and survivor payments to qualified people.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"> <!-- 8th -->
        <div class="card-header card-header-even" id="heading8">
          <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse8">
            <h4>Immigration and Nationality Act</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse8" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading8" data-parent="#accordionE">
          <div class="card-body card-content-even">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-4">
                <img src="photos/federal_laws/immigrationact.jpg" />
              </div>
              <div class="col-8">
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h5>Specifies the standards for issuing visas and other immigration benefits and regulates immigration to the United States.</h5>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
